The package boost-ptr-container is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS ptr_container)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::ptr_container)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_ptr_container REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::ptr_container)
